  "title": "Senior Accountant",
  "description": "<p>- Preparation for full set of accounts for clients<br />- Preparation of accounting schedules<br />- Assist in client yearly audit<br />- Preparation of payroll, CPF/IR8A form, individual tax for clients<br />- Preparation of GST reports and submission to IRAS for clients<br />- Computation of local taxes, submission of tax filing and compliance with local tax regulations for clients<br />- Preparation of unaudited financial statements<br />- Other duties and responsibilities as assigned by manager<br /></p><p>Job Requirements:<br />- Degree in Accountancy/ACCA<br />- 5-6 years of relevant experience in auditing or accounting/tax preparation for third party clients<br />- Strong analytical and problem-solving skills<br />- Able to use: MYOB, XERO, NAV<br />- Ex-auditors are welcome</p><p>Qualified or interested candidates, please send your updated resume in WORDS format, stating the following : -<br />- Availability<br />- Current / last drawn salaries<br />- Reasons for leaving previous employment<br />- Expected Salary<br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.\n</p>",
