    "description": "<p>Morningstar Management offers a comprehensive range of company incorporation, accounting, tax advisory, human resources, audit and consultancy services to business in various field. Our team of &nbsp;highly reliable and professional tax advisor and auditor provides highly customized solutions to bring our clients' business forward since 2017.<br>\n<br>\nWe commit to offer on-job training, long term career advancement and personal growth. As part of our growth strategy, we are looking for outstanding and motivated individuals to join our team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>When you work with us, you will work with people who care deeply about your career advancement and have greater access to senior expertise.</p>",
